consideration the available workforce provided by permanent employees and the department’s performance targets; and
82. Require the COS/ JO workers to provide accomplishment reports which are quantifiable and traceable to their department’s/section’s performance targets; and
83. Establish a sound control system in monitoring the attendance of each personnel, particularly of JO workers, and/or install an automated attendance monitoring
tool to keep track of their attendance.

