We recommended that the Municipal Mayor:

a. Direct the Local School Board of the Municipality to formulate a three-year program;

b. Require the person in-charge to submit to the audit team the Local School Board Resolution approving the CY 2024 SEF Budget;

c. Direct the LSB to review and approve the SEF Budget for the ensuing year through an LSB Resolution approved by the majority of all LSB members not later than October 31 of the current year;

