3. Ensure that no procurement shall be authorized and undertaken unless it is in accordance with an approved APP or supplemental APP; and
4. Instruct all officials and employees to purchase airline tickets directly from commercial airlines and service providers as provided under Section V, Item b of Annex H of the Revised IRR of RA No. 9184.

