b. Direct the GSO strictly monitor the POs/contracts delivery dates and coordinate with the Municipal Accountant if delays are incurred by suppliers;
c. Direct the Municipal Accountant to be circumspect in the processing of claims so that liquidated damages could be imposed; and
d. Ensure strict adherence to Section 6.8 and Item 3.1, Annex D of the Revised IRR of RA No. 9184 in the implementation of procurement contracts.

