Judiciously plan and assess the need of hiring a consultant to avoid duplication of functions with regular plantilla personnel of the LGUs;
Prepare and submit all relevant supporting documents from procurement until payment of consultants;
Strictly observe the rules and regulations on the withholding of applicable taxes for consultancy services to avoid adverse actions in audit; and
Strictly observe the provisions of COA Circular No. 2015-009 on the use of proper accounts in recording government transactions.

